        "generateUrl": "https://developers.webflow.com/data/reference/oauth-app",
        "setup": "In the Webflow developer docs, use the [OAuth app](https://developers.webflow.com/data/reference/oauth-app) flow from the [Data API authentication docs](https://developers.webflow.com/data/reference/authentication) to register an app in Webflow and authorize it for the needed scopes. Use the resulting access token against Webflow APIs and the MCP server."
